{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260224/1102914374441373696058732.jpeg/8Tql5gJu4pUDO8QW6dc9YL22ombJD4hofc5LlX3OS5U\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\"><p>4月23日，歐盟宣布撤銷對中國兩家金融機構的制裁，商務部稱據《中華人民共和國反外國制裁法》《實施〈中華人民共和國反外國制裁法〉的規定》等法律法規，取消對歐盟兩家金融機構的反制措施。</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T14:55:31.471772+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":90,"images":1,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}